A family in Gitithia village, Lari constituency, wants Chief Justice David Maraga to solve a 30-year-old land dispute. John Kariuki (pictured) said the case has not been mentioned or heard this year.He said the dispute started when their late father Thuo Matheri sold a portion of their land in 1986. &ldquo;We live there not knowing what will happen,&rdquo; the 80-year-old said.